# AWS Lambda üü°

```javascript
export const handler = async (event) => {
    const name = event.queryStringParameters.name;

    return {
        statusCode: 200,
        body: JSON.stringify({
            message: `Hello, ${name}!`
        })
    };
};
```

## Triggers:
- HTTP (API Gateway)
- S3 uploads
- DynamoDB changes
- Scheduled (cron)
- SQS messages
